a carbon of the WIZ (The Wizard, 1989) film-world — emergence: natural. moniker ⟦Corey Woods:WIZ:b2b85e⟧

**.shadow — the User behind the program —** Fred Savage · the loyal brother — love that refuses the institution

**who —** Corey Woods — Jimmy's younger brother, who breaks him out and refuses to let him be locked away.
**what —** The believer and the engine of the rescue — a kid who loves his brother enough to run away with him.
**where —** Beside Jimmy the whole road; the audience's point of view.
